#

Smoky Chipotle BBQ Pulled Pork

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

Comfort FoodBBQSlow-Cooked

Description

Tender pulled pork infused with a smoky chipotle BBQ sauce, perfect for sandwiches or served with coleslaw.

Ingredients

  • Pork Shoulder: 4 lbs
  • Smoked Paprika: 2 tbsp
  • Chipotle Powder: 1 tbsp
  • Garlic Powder: 1 tbsp
  • Onion Powder: 1 tbsp
  • Brown Sugar: 1/4 cup
  • Apple Cider Vinegar: 1 cup
  • BBQ Sauce: 2 cups
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
  • Coleslaw Mix: 4 cups
